OL,5,G2345 Black Sabbath: Classic Albums
OL,6,     FThe story behind the writing,
OL,7,     Frecording and success of Black
OL,8,     FSabbath's second album, Paranoid,
OL,9,     Fone of the most influential albums
OL,10,     Fof the heavy metal genre.
OL,11,G0100 The Warhol Effect
OL,12,     FFilm lifting the lid on the
OL,13,     Ffascinating last decade of Andy
OL,14,     FWarhol's life and the legacy he
OL,15,     Fleft for future artists, through
OL,16,     Fnever-before-seen footage and
OL,17,     Finterviews with insiders.
